query:
SELECT MIN(k.keyword) AS movie_keyword, MIN(n.name) AS actor_name, MIN(t.title) AS marvel_movie
 FROM cast_info AS ci,
 keyword AS k,
 movie_keyword AS mk,
 name AS n,
 title AS t
 WHERE k.id = mk.keyword_id
 AND t.id = mk.movie_id
 AND t.id = ci.movie_id
 AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
 AND n.id = ci.person_id
 AND k.keyword = 'question-in-title'
 AND n.name LIKE '%,%'
 AND t.production_year > 1999;
plan_content: /*+  SeqScan(t) SeqScan(k) IndexScan(mk keyword_id_movie_keyword) IndexScan(ci movie_id_cast_info) SeqScan(n) NestLoop(k mk) HashJoin(t k mk) NestLoop(t k mk ci) HashJoin(t k mk ci n) Leading((((t (k mk)) ci) n)) */
